      "message": "I reviewed the PDI and noticed that the controlled_by association used in this patch — from the GPU inventory path to the Power.Cap object — is not formally defined in xyz/openbmc_project/Control/Power/Cap.interface.yaml. The spec only defines the\n  controlling/controlled_by association with xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Item.Chassis as the required endpoint interface, not Inventory.Item.Accelerator.\n\nI will address this by either adding Inventory.Item.Accelerator to the PDI\n\nAlso, I have tested and reviewed your change 87955. It does not affect the /redfish/v1/Systems/\u003cstr\u003e/Processors/GPU_*/EnvironmentMetrics path, and I think the refactoring looks great",
